00:05:27.550 --> 00:05:29.870 align:middle line:10%
>>You want to begin
to see your experience

00:05:29.870 --> 00:05:33.650 align:middle line:10%
as part and parcel
of a continuum.

00:05:33.650 --> 00:05:36.250 align:middle line:10%
So the continuum that
I'm speaking about

00:05:36.250 --> 00:05:39.516 align:middle line:10%
began with the first cause, or
when the universe was created,

00:05:39.516 --> 00:05:40.890 align:middle line:10%
when something
came from nothing.

00:05:40.890 --> 00:05:43.760 align:middle line:10%
That's when the
whole process began.

00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:46.360 align:middle line:10%
So that's when this continuum,
that's when time began.

00:05:46.360 --> 00:05:49.920 align:middle line:10%
And so we want to
begin to learn how

00:05:49.920 --> 00:05:53.980 align:middle line:10%
to see your own experience
as the leading edge.

00:05:53.980 --> 00:06:00.980 align:middle line:10%
As the most sophisticated most
complex expression of a process

00:06:00.980 --> 00:06:02.540 align:middle line:10%
that started 14
billion years ago.

00:06:02.540 --> 00:06:13.470 align:middle line:90%


00:06:13.470 --> 00:06:15.814 align:middle line:10%
And when you really
begin to get this--

00:06:15.814 --> 00:06:17.480 align:middle line:10%
not just at a rational
level, but that's

00:06:17.480 --> 00:06:18.680 align:middle line:10%
a good place to start.

00:06:18.680 --> 00:06:21.170 align:middle line:10%
But when you begin
to see it and feel it

00:06:21.170 --> 00:06:24.270 align:middle line:10%
you begin to relate your own
experience of being alive,

00:06:24.270 --> 00:06:25.810 align:middle line:10%
your own experience
of consciousness

00:06:25.810 --> 00:06:39.060 align:middle line:10%
to the evolution of the cosmos

00:06:39.060 --> 00:06:40.760 align:middle line:10%
So the reason why
this is so important,

00:06:40.760 --> 00:06:45.050 align:middle line:10%
this particular time in history,
is because more and more of us

00:06:45.050 --> 00:06:46.306 align:middle line:10%
have to begin to get this.

00:06:46.306 --> 00:06:47.806 align:middle line:10%
So we're going to
pull ourselves out

00:06:47.806 --> 00:06:50.680 align:middle line:10%
of this narcissistic
nightmare and discover

00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:53.760 align:middle line:10%
the inherently thrilling
nature and the sense

00:06:53.760 --> 00:06:57.040 align:middle line:10%
of ultimate sacred
importance of who we are,

00:06:57.040 --> 00:07:00.240 align:middle line:10%
and what we're a part of,
and what we can actually do.

00:07:00.240 --> 00:07:07.410 align:middle line:90%


00:07:07.410 --> 00:07:08.370 align:middle line:90%
