00:21:36.240 --> 00:21:41.730 align:middle line:10%
convinced in the overwhelmingly
positive nature of existence?

00:21:41.730 --> 00:21:44.690 align:middle line:10%
What if you were
convinced beyond any doubt

00:21:44.690 --> 00:21:48.480 align:middle line:10%
whatsoever that
to exist is good.

00:21:48.480 --> 00:21:52.170 align:middle line:84%
That the will towards
existence is positive.

00:21:52.170 --> 00:21:56.950 align:middle line:10%
A lot of people aren't so sure,
because they say, well look.

00:21:56.950 --> 00:21:59.370 align:middle line:10%
There's poverty,
there's inequality,

00:21:59.370 --> 00:22:03.170 align:middle line:10%
there's environmental
degradation, there's fascism,

00:22:03.170 --> 00:22:05.400 align:middle line:10%
