things happen in the world.

00:22:05.400 --> 00:22:09.010 align:middle line:10%
And nature, look
what nature is doing.

00:22:09.010 --> 00:22:11.980 align:middle line:10%
Nature has tsunamis,
and volcanoes, I mean,

00:22:11.980 --> 00:22:13.480 align:middle line:10%
it's a very dangerous
