00:22:13.480 --> 00:22:14.980 align:middle line:10%
Well, life is a
kind of dicey thing,

00:22:14.980 --> 00:22:16.646 align:middle line:10%
you don't know what
you're going to get.

00:22:16.646 --> 00:22:19.590 align:middle line:10%
If we look at all these
particular problems, and all

00:22:19.590 --> 00:22:23.995 align:middle line:10%
these unpleasant and nasty
and horrible things that

00:22:23.995 --> 00:22:28.380 align:middle line:10%
can happen, do happen,
will happen, have always

00:22:28.380 --> 00:22:31.390 align:middle line:10%
been part of the
process, suddenly we're

00:22:31.390 --> 00:22:33.470 align:middle line:10%
not so sure that to
exist is too good.

00:22:33.470 --> 00:22:35.720 align:middle line:84%
Because, oh, well,
living to exist is good,

00:22:35.720 --> 00:22:39.257 align:middle line:84%
but then there's pain, there's
suffering, there's death.

00:22:39.257 --> 00:22:41.090 align:middle line:10%
What about all that,
why is there suffering?

00:22:41.090 --> 00:22:43.340 align:middle line:10%
How could God exist as
long as there's pain?

00:22:43.340 --> 00:22:45.104 align:middle line:10%
That kind of thing, right?

00:22:45.104 --> 00:22:47.020 align:middle line:10%
So what if in the midst
of all this complexity

00:22:47.020 --> 00:22:50.550 align:middle line:10%
and adversity if you
knew without any doubt

00:22:50.550 --> 00:22:53.500 align:middle line:10%
that the urge to
exist, which relates

00:22:53.500 --> 00:22:56.980 align:middle line:10%
to the Big Bang-- I interpret
the Big Bang as the desire

00:22:56.980 --> 00:22:58.887 align:middle line:10%
to exist in time and in form.

00:22:58.887 --> 00:23:01.470 align:middle line:10%
So what if you knew without any
doubt that the desire to exist

00:23:01.470 --> 00:23:03.337 align:middle line:10%
was overwhelmingly
positive in spite

00:23:03.337 --> 00:23:04.920 align:middle line:10%
of all the terrible
things that happen

00:23:04.920 --> 00:23:06.336 align:middle line:10%
in the process in
the midst of it?

00:23:06.336 --> 00:23:09.407 align:middle line:10%
But if you knew that
the will to exist

00:23:09.407 --> 00:23:11.740 align:middle line:10%
which started with the Big
Bang, and which we experience

00:23:11.740 --> 00:23:14.460 align:middle line:10%
as the sexual impulses,
the creative impulse,

00:23:14.460 --> 00:23:17.555 align:middle line:10%
as creative inspiration,
that the will to exist,

00:23:17.555 --> 00:23:21.180 align:middle line:10%
the will towards life, and
the will towards creativity

00:23:21.180 --> 00:23:23.250 align:middle line:10%
is overwhelmingly positive.

00:23:23.250 --> 00:23:25.010 align:middle line:10%
It's absolutely
positive and good.

00:23:25.010 --> 00:23:28.360 align:middle line:10%
Would that change your
relationship to life?

00:23:28.360 --> 00:23:31.550 align:middle line:10%
Because you know
that life is good.

00:23:31.550 --> 00:23:33.930 align:middle line:84%
Even though bad stuff happens,
you still now that life

00:23:33.930 --> 00:23:34.430 align:middle line:90%
is good.

00:23:34.430 --> 00:23:37.397 align:middle line:90%
The will to exist is good.

00:23:37.397 --> 00:23:38.230 align:middle line:90%
