heal woundedness is

00:23:46.810 --> 00:23:50.010 align:middle line:84%
to realize that the
deepest part of who you are

00:23:50.010 --> 00:23:52.100 align:middle line:84%
has never been hurt,
wounded or traumatized

00:23:52.100 --> 00:23:53.295 align:middle line:90%
by anyone or anything.

00:23:53.295 --> 00:23:55.124 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow, wow.

00:23:55.124 --> 00:23:57.540 align:middle line:84%
>>COHEN: The deepest part of
the self has never been born,

00:23:57.540 --> 00:23:59.081 align:middle line:84%
and never entered
the stream of time,

00:23:59.081 --> 00:24:01.120 align:middle line:84%
and therefore is
untouched by anything

00:24:01.120 --> 00:24:03.310 align:middle line:90%
that's ever happened in time.

00:24:03.310 --> 00:24:06.790 align:middle line:84%
And simultaneously, we can say
the energy and intelligence

00:24:06.790 --> 00:24:09.250 align:middle line:84%
that created the universe
and is creating the universe,

00:24:09.250 --> 00:24:12.130 align:middle line:84%
the creative force in the
universe, called Eros,

00:24:12.130 --> 00:24:13.050 align:middle line:90%
is indestructible.

00:24:13.050 --> 00:24:15.520 align:middle line:84%
It can't be hurt,
wounded, or traumatized

00:24:15.520 --> 00:24:17.120 align:middle line:90%
by anyone or anything.

00:24:17.120 --> 00:24:18.960 align:middle line:90%
It can't be stopped.

00:24:18.960 --> 00:24:21.600 align:middle line:84%
So what we do is we
learn how to begin

00:24:21.600 --> 00:24:25.470 align:middle line:84%
to identify with these
deeper dimensions of ourself,

00:24:25.470 --> 00:24:29.110 align:middle line:84%
and to begin to identify
less with these more

00:24:29.110 --> 00:24:31.450 align:middle line:90%
relative dimensions of the self.

00:24:31.450 --> 00:24:35.260 align:middle line:84%
And we begin to take our
woundedness a lot less

00:24:35.260 --> 00:24:36.800 align:middle line:90%
seriously.

00:24:36.800 --> 00:24:38.900 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's actually
beautifully said, Andrew.

00:24:38.900 --> 00:24:42.950 align:middle line:84%
Is that the deepest, truest part
of us was never really wounded.

00:24:42.950 --> 00:24:44.706 align:middle line:90%
Very, very powerful words.

00:24:44.706 --> 00:24:45.580 align:middle line:90%
We're going to come--

00:24:45.580 --> 00:24:46.570 align:middle line:84%
>>COHEN: It's a
shift of identity.

00:24:46.570 --> 00:24:47.945 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It's a
shift of identity.

00:24:47.945 --> 00:24:50.272 align:middle line:84%
And it's letting
go of our story.

00:24:50.272 --> 00:24:52.230 align:middle line:84%
And it's getting over
those and looking at them

00:24:52.230 --> 00:24:56.064 align:middle line:84%
as speed bumps in our overall
Evolutionary Enlightenment.

00:24:56.064 --> 00:24:57.980 align:middle line:84%
>>COHEN: Being willing
to let go of our story.

00:24:57.980 --> 00:24:58.880 align:middle line:90%
Being willing to.

00:24:58.880 --> 00:24:59.921 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Being willing to.

