00:27:12.647 --> 00:27:14.730 align:middle line:84%
And this is something that
most people don't know.

00:27:14.730 --> 00:27:15.210 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: No.

00:27:15.210 --> 00:27:17.418 align:middle line:84%
>>COHEN: If that's not ever
