But there's actually less of
that going on, comparatively?

00:27:34.850 --> 00:27:37.756 align:middle line:84%
>>COHEN: Apparently,
much, much less.

00:27:37.756 --> 00:27:39.130 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So now
how does this have

00:27:39.130 --> 00:27:42.311 align:middle line:84%
to do with us being the
