00:27:42.311 --> 00:27:43.810 align:middle line:84%
>>COHEN: Well, I
guess what it would

00:27:43.810 --> 00:27:48.110 align:middle line:84%
have to do with that is that
you and I are living in an era

00:27:48.110 --> 00:27:51.140 align:middle line:84%
where, in this case, violence
has been on the decrease,

00:27:51.140 --> 00:27:55.270 align:middle line:84%
but most importantly, there are
