00:27:55.270 --> 00:28:00.310 align:middle line:84%
of us who are experiencing
a level of good fortune

00:28:00.310 --> 00:28:02.140 align:middle line:84%
that's historically
unprecedented.

00:28:02.140 --> 00:28:05.150 align:middle line:84%
The problem is most of us
don't seem to feel very lucky

00:28:05.150 --> 00:28:07.890 align:middle line:84%
