luckiest people that have ever

00:28:07.890 --> 00:28:08.640 align:middle line:90%
been born.

00:28:08.640 --> 00:28:11.180 align:middle line:84%
And that, to me,
shows that there's

00:28:11.180 --> 00:28:13.600 align:middle line:84%
a spiritual crisis at
the level of culture,

00:28:13.600 --> 00:28:16.480 align:middle line:84%
if someone who's very fortunate
doesn't feel fortunate.

00:28:16.480 --> 00:28:20.150 align:middle line:84%
And too many of us feel stressed
out and very victimized.

00:28:20.150 --> 00:28:22.090 align:middle line:84%
We don't really--
because if you know

00:28:22.090 --> 00:28:24.423 align:middle line:84%
you're one of the luckiest
people that's ever been born,

00:28:24.423 --> 00:28:26.550 align:middle line:84%
you feel lucky,
