00:28:45.710 --> 00:28:47.780 align:middle line:84%
about everybody else
and this big process

00:28:47.780 --> 00:28:48.860 align:middle line:90%
that we're a part of.

00:28:48.860 --> 00:28:52.300 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So that ultimately is
Evolutionary Enlightenment.

