00:44:06.700 --> 00:44:09.620 align:middle line:84%
So in taking these
types of-- this

00:44:09.620 --> 00:44:13.130 align:middle line:84%
is basically the evolution
of politics, if you will.

00:44:13.130 --> 00:44:16.070 align:middle line:84%
>>COHEN: Well, we're facing
enormous difficulties

00:44:16.070 --> 00:44:17.720 align:middle line:84%
