evolve and develop.

00:45:39.097 --> 00:45:39.930 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Fascinating.

00:45:39.930 --> 00:45:42.720 align:middle line:84%
So it goes along
with the fifth tenet,

00:45:42.720 --> 00:45:44.477 align:middle line:84%
