consciousness.

00:45:44.477 --> 00:45:45.560 align:middle line:90%
>>COHEN: Cosmic conscious.

00:45:45.560 --> 00:45:47.380 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Conscience, sorry.

00:45:47.380 --> 00:45:49.750 align:middle line:84%
>>COHEN: Cosmic conscience
