00:46:05.340 --> 00:46:06.594 align:middle line:90%
That's who I really am.

00:46:06.594 --> 00:46:08.010 align:middle line:84%
That's the energy
and intelligence

00:46:08.010 --> 00:46:13.650 align:middle line:84%
